'''詹姆斯·沃德-普勞斯'''（{{lang-en|'''James Ward-Prowse'''}}，{{bd|1994年|11月1日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球運動員，在場上司職[[中場|中場]]，現在效力於[[英超|英超]]球隊[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|南安普顿]]並擔任隊長，也代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭足球代表隊]]參賽。他出身自{{link-en|南安普敦青訓營|Southampton F.C. Academy}}。場上位置是[[中場|中場中路]]或右邊鋒。

==早期生涯和個人生活==
沃德-普勞斯出生在[[朴茨茅斯|朴茨茅斯]]。他的父親約翰·沃德-普勞斯<ref name=Echo271011>{{cite web|last=Walter|first=Simon|title=Why teenager James ditched Pompey for Saints|url=http://www.dailyecho.co.uk/sport/saints/news/9328132.Why_teenager_James_ditched_Pompey_for_Saints/|publisher=Southern Echo|accessdate=27 October 2011|date=27 October 2011|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329222845/https://www.dailyecho.co.uk/sport/saints/news/9328132.Why_teenager_James_ditched_Pompey_for_Saints/|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一位出庭律師<ref>{{cite web |title=John Ward-Prowse |url=http://www.legalhub.co.uk/legalhub/app/init/signon?redirect=%252Flegalhub%252Fapp%252Fdocument%253Frs%253DBOL1.0%2526vr%253D1.0%2526src%253Dri%2526docguid%253DIe21bd8d18bcb11dcaa9aaaaa0e13eb96%2526suppsrguid%253Dia744dc2100000118372abf56ccbf3fb0%2526spos%253D4%2526epos%253D4%2526td%253D4%2526ctype%253D%2526bctocguid%253DI369f4260639711dba7e5e11db8d74eba%2526bchistory%253D5%253B6%253B%2526ststate%253DS%253BS%2526linktype%253Dref%2526toc-search%253D&vr=1.0&wluk-usertype=&wluk-usertype=&rs=BOL1.0 |publisher=Legal Hub |accessdate=27 October 2011 |archive-date=2016-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630032712/http://www.legalhub.co.uk/legalhub/app/init/signon?redirect=%252Flegalhub%252Fapp%252Fdocument%253Frs%253DBOL1.0%2526vr%253D1.0%2526src%253Dri%2526docguid%253DIe21bd8d18bcb11dcaa9aaaaa0e13eb96%2526suppsrguid%253Dia744dc2100000118372abf56ccbf3fb0%2526spos%253D4%2526epos%253D4%2526td%253D4%2526ctype%253D%2526bctocguid%253DI369f4260639711dba7e5e11db8d74eba%2526bchistory%253D5%253B6%253B%2526ststate%253DS%253BS%2526linktype%253Dref%2526toc-search%253D&vr=1.0&wluk-usertype=&wluk-usertype=&rs=BOL1.0 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。雖然他的家庭是[[樸茨茅斯足球俱樂部|朴茨茅斯]]的球迷<ref name=Echo271011/>，但他卻在八歲時加入了朴茨茅斯的對手[[南安普敦足球俱樂部|南安普敦]]<ref name=officialprofile>{{cite web|url=https://southamptonfc.com/first-team/ward-prowse|title=James Ward-Prowse|publisher=Southampton F.C.|accessdate=11 September 2013|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116092049/https://www.southamptonfc.com/first-team/ward-prowse|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

沃德-普勞斯和他的伴侶奧利維亞有一個兒子叫奧斯卡，於2018年出生。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Winter |first1=Henry |title=Southampton’s James Ward-Prowse: It’s not about being first – we must protect jobs |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/southamptons-james-ward-prowse-we-wanted-to-protect-the-club-and-look-after-the-local-community-5gjnrwhsg |access-date=19 November 2020 |work=The Times |date=13 April 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128053617/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/southamptons-james-ward-prowse-we-wanted-to-protect-the-club-and-look-after-the-local-community-5gjnrwhsg |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==俱樂部生涯==
沃德-普勞斯在八歲時加入{{link-en|南安普敦青訓營|Southampton F.C. Academy}}。在2010-11賽季，他在南安普敦的U18隊表現突出<ref name="officialprofile"/>。2011年10月，在沃德-普勞斯16歲時，他首次代表南安普敦成人隊出場。他代表南安普敦一隊出場的第一場比賽是2011-12賽季聯賽盃南安普敦對[[水晶宮足球俱樂部|水晶宮]]的比賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/15432969 |title=Nigel Adkins backs 16-year-old Southampton debutant |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=24 October 2011 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2014-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228153134/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/15432969 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/15346395 |title=Crystal Palace 2–0 Southampton |last=Smith |first=Chris |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=24 October 2011 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2014-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228153236/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/15346395 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2053405/Crystal-Palace-2-Southampton-0-Darren-Ambrose-Jermaine-Easter-help-Eagles-soar-eight.html |title=Crystal Palace 2 Southampton 0: Williams is the spark as Eagles leave it late |last=Butler |first=Matt |publisher=''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]'' |date=26 October 2011 |accessdate=14 September 2013 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809232048/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2053405/Crystal-Palace-2-Southampton-0-Darren-Ambrose-Jermaine-Easter-help-Eagles-soar-eight.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。沃德-普勞斯在他第二次代表南安普敦一隊出場時打入了自己在一隊的首個進球。這是[[2011/12球季英格蘭足總盃|2011/12球季英格蘭足總盃]]南安普敦對[[考文垂足球俱樂部|考文垂]]的一場比賽，南安普敦憑藉這個進球以2–1戰勝對手，晉級第四輪<ref name="officialprofile"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/16371777 |title=Coventry 1–2 Southampton |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=7 January 2012 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2014-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228225321/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/16371777 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2083591/Coventry-1-Southampton-2-Sky-Blues-dumped-youthful-Saints-side.html |title=Coventry 1 Southampton 2: Sky Blues dumped out by youthful Saints side |publisher=''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]'' |date=7 January 2012 |accessdate=14 September 2013 |archive-date=2017-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224220729/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2083591/Coventry-1-Southampton-2-Sky-Blues-dumped-youthful-Saints-side.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年5月，隨著南安普敦重返英超，沃德-普勞斯成為四位獲得新職業合同的南安普敦青年隊球員之一（另外三位是[[杰克·斯蒂芬斯|斯蒂芬斯]]、[[魯克·梳爾|梳爾]]、[[卡林·張伯斯|張伯斯]]）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18176183 |title=Southampton promote academy quartet to first team squad |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=23 May 2012 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2013-01-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DxnAI5dz?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18176183 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===2012–13賽季===
沃德-普勞斯新的球衣號碼是16號，並且在[[修咸頓2012年至2013年球季|2012–13賽季]]揭幕戰首次代表南安普敦在[[英超|英超]]聯賽中出場。他在這場比賽的前65分鐘出場，這場比賽南安普敦最終以3–2不敵衛冕冠軍[[曼徹斯特城足球俱樂部|曼城]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19231354 |title=Man City 3–2 Southampton |last=Bevan |first=Chris |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=19 August 2012 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2012-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120820012732/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19231354 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。賽后主教練[[尼祖·艾堅斯|尼祖·艾堅斯]]用「卓越」一詞形容沃德-普勞斯的表現<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19314119 |title=Southampton boss Adkins defends starting Rickie Lambert on bench |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=19 August 2012 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2015-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522042836/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19314119 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在對[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|維根競技]]的比賽替補出場之後<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19304275 |title=Southampton 0–2 Wigan |last=Monaghan |first=Matt |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=25 August 2012 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2016-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121115059/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19304275 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這位17歲小將在他的第三場英超比賽南安普敦對[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]的比賽中再次首發出場，並且繼續在評論家之間得到好評 <ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19384117 |title=Southampton 2–3 Man Utd |last=Hassan |first=Nabil |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=2 September 2012 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2012-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106022701/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19384117 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在這一年的11月，沃德-普勞斯在他過18歲之後不久從南安普敦獲得了一份新的五年合同，但也有流言炒作他將在不久的將來離開南安普敦<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20403062 |title=Southampton secure James Ward-Prowse on five-year deal |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=19 November 2012 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2014-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140501171320/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20403062 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2235415/James-Ward-Prowse-signs-new-Southampton-deal.html |title=Rising Saints star Ward-Prowse pens long-term deal at St Mary's |last=Hirst |first=Paul |publisher=''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]'' |date=19 November 2012 |accessdate=14 September 2013 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003945/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2235415/James-Ward-Prowse-signs-new-Southampton-deal.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年2月，沃德-普勞斯曾被短暫外借至[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]球隊[[考文垂足球俱樂部|考文垂]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/southampton-transfer-news-james-ward-prowse-1573189 |title=Sent to Coventry: James Ward-Prowse set to leave Southampton on loan |publisher=''[[Daily_Mirror|Daily Mirror]]'' |date=3 February 2013 |accessdate=14 September 2013 |archive-date=2017-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171229231617/http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/southampton-transfer-news-james-ward-prowse-1573189 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在三月南安普敦主場對[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|女王公园巡游者]]的一場比賽中，沃德-普勞斯傳球中後衛[[吉田麻也|吉田麻也]]，但由於替補門將[[罗伯特·格林|罗伯特·格林]]的精彩表現扑出了吉田的射門，女王公园巡游者得以在客場帶走三分<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21556942 |title=Southampton 1–2 QPR |last=Sheringham |first=Sam |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=2 March 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2016-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123134616/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21556942 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他之後在5月12日英超倒數第二輪南安普敦對[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|桑德兰]]的比賽中助攻[[杰森·宾捷安|杰森·宾捷安]]打入扳平比分的一球，為南安普敦奪得重要一分<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22417765 |title=Sunderland 1–1 Southampton |last=Ornstein |first=David |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=12 May 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017192947/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22417765 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

儘管沃德-普勞斯在這一賽季為俱樂部出場15次，但許多時候都是作為替補登場。賽季結束後，媒體評論沃德-普勞斯「不滿足只坐在板凳上」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22855248 |title=Southampton: James Ward-Prowse desperate for game time |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=11 June 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102222131/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22855248 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在五月份，沃德-普勞斯戰勝隊友[[魯克·梳爾|梳爾]]和[[多米尼克·蓋普|蓋普]]，獲得了南安普敦賽季獎學金榮譽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.saintsfc.co.uk/news/article/morgan-does-the-double-821815.aspx |title=Morgan Does the Double! |publisher=Southampton F.C. |date=14 May 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705012423/http://www.saintsfc.co.uk/news/article/morgan-does-the-double-821815.aspx |archive-date=2015-07-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===2013–14賽季===
在[[修咸頓2013年至2014年球季|2013–14賽季]]之初，曾短暫有流言稱沃德-普勞斯可能被租借至[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球隊[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|伯恩茅斯]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailyecho.co.uk/sport/10493233._/ |title=Ward-Prowse linked with Cherries loan move |last=Carter |first=Simon |publisher=''Southern Daily Echo'' |date=19 June 2013 |accessdate=14 September 2013 |archive-date=2017-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304051830/http://www.dailyecho.co.uk/sport/10493233._/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。沃德-普勞斯在本賽季的首場比賽南安普敦對[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗維奇]]的比賽中就有出色表現，獲得了主教練[[毛里西奥·波切蒂諾|毛里西奥·波切蒂諾]]的青睞<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23644676 |title=West Brom 0–1 Southampton |last=Johnston |first=Neil |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=17 August 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2016-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118195538/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23644676 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。沃德-普勞斯還在之後南安普敦對桑德蘭的比賽中打滿全場，並在第88分鐘時助攻[[何塞·馮特|何塞·馮特]]打入扳平一球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23737155 |title=Southampton 1–1 Sunderland |last=Hassan |first=Neil |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=24 August 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2016-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118123550/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23737155 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===2014–15賽季===
在2014年9月20日之前，由於在戰勝[[斯旺西城足球俱樂部|斯旺西]]的比賽中腳部骨折，沃德-普勞斯休戰10週<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29338750|title=Southampton's James Ward-Prowse out for 10 weeks|date=23 September 2014|accessdate=24 September 2014|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704044001/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29338750|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月，他和俱樂部簽訂了一份新的為期五年半的合同<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31058841|title=James Ward-Prowse signs new long-term Southampton deal|date=30 January 2015|accessdate=30 January 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2015-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210051841/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31058841|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月11日，他在南安普敦2–0戰勝[[赫爾城足球俱樂部|赫爾城]]的比賽中打入自己在英超的首個進球<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32179964|title=Southampton 2-0 Hull City|date=11 April 2015|accessdate=11 April 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702153844/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32179964|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在5月2日南安普敦對桑德蘭的比賽中，他得到一張紅牌<ref>{{cite news|title=Sunderland 2-1 Southampton|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32460246|accessdate=3 May 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=2 May 2015|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627081352/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32460246|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2019–20賽季===
2020年6月，沃德-普勞斯取代了[[皮埃尔·霍伊别尔|皮埃爾-埃米爾·霍伊別爾]]擔任南安普敦隊長，最初一直到2019-20賽季結束。2020年8月17日，沃德-普勞斯簽訂了新合約，直到2025年6月。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/53803879 |title=James Ward-Prowse: Southampton captain signs new five-year deal |website=BBC Sport |date=17 August 2020 |access-date=17 August 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903214709/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/53803879 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==國家隊生涯==
沃德-普勞斯的國家隊生涯開始於[[英格蘭17歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U17國家隊]]。在2010年至2011年，他代表英格蘭U17出場7次<ref name="england">{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/All-Teams/Players/W/James-Ward-Prowse |title=James Ward-Prowse |work=England Players |publisher=The Football Association |accessdate=14 September 2013 |archive-date=2014-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009195754/http://www.thefa.com/england/all-teams/players/w/james-ward-prowse |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年，他進入[[英格蘭19歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U19國家隊]]。他共代表英格蘭U19國家隊出場4次。2013年，他代表[[英格蘭20歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U20國家隊]]參加了在土耳其舉辦的[[2013年U20世界盃足球賽|2013年U20世界盃足球賽]]<ref name="england"/>。

2013年8月，沃德-普勞斯在他18歲時被召入[[盖雷斯·索斯盖特|索斯盖特]]的[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21國家隊]]，參加了[[2015年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2015年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]英格蘭對[[摩爾多瓦21歲以下國家足球隊|摩爾多瓦U21國家隊]]和[[芬蘭21歲以下國家足球隊|芬蘭U21國家隊]]的預選賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23854578 |title=James Ward-Prowse gets first England Under-21s call-up |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=27 August 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2015-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509031729/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23854578 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在第一場比賽中上場64分鐘<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23981048 |title=England U21s beat Moldova in Gareth Southgate's first game |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=5 September 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017062701/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23981048 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，對芬蘭的比賽中他打滿全場<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24025201 |title=Saido Berahino nets in England U21 draw with Finland |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=9 September 2013 |accessdate=11 September 2013 |archive-date=2013-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115051112/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24025201 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在10月15日英格蘭對[[立陶宛21歲以下國家足球隊|立陶宛]]的比賽中，他打入了自己在英格蘭U21的首個進球。這是一個距球迷20碼的任意球<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24540949 "England U21 5–0 Lithuania U21"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24540949 |date=20131019172555 }} BBC Sport. 15 October 2013. Retrieved 16 October 2013.</ref>。在2014年土倫杯英格蘭對巴西的小組賽中，他打入了一個「絕妙的」任意球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/under-21/2014/may/james-ward-prowse-brazil-reaction-270514 |title=James Ward-Prowse wishes free-kick was the winner |publisher=The FA |date=27 May 2014 |accessdate=28 May 2014 |archive-date=2014-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529051321/http://www.thefa.com/news/england/under-21/2014/may/james-ward-prowse-brazil-reaction-270514 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個進球之後被投票選為本屆賽事最佳進球。沃德-普勞斯也被選為本屆土倫杯最佳球員之一<ref>{{cite web|last1=Urquhart-Cannon|first1=Alex|title=Ward-Prowse wins two Toulon trophies|url=http://www.saintsfc.co.uk/news/article/02062014-jwp-toulon-prizes-1593524.aspx|publisher=Southampton FC|accessdate=3 June 2014|date=2 June 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924093828/http://www.saintsfc.co.uk/news/article/02062014-jwp-toulon-prizes-1593524.aspx|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2015年4月，[[羅伊·霍奇森|霍奇森]]稱沃德-普勞斯是「希望人選」，並暗示沃德-普勞斯很有希望進入英格蘭一隊<ref>{{cite web|title=Southampton's Ward-Prowse is a "big prospect", says Roy Hodgson|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/32183150|publisher=BBC|accessdate=17 June 2015|date=4 April 2014|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924222903/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/32183150|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年9月5日，沃德-普勞斯睽違已久再次入選[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭足球代表隊]]名單。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/53955829 |title=Iceland 0–1 England |first=Phil |last=McNulty |website=BBC Sport |date=5 September 2020 |access-date=6 September 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925034741/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/53955829/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年3月25日，沃德-普勞斯在[[2022年國際足總世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|2022年世界盃外圍賽]]對陣[[聖馬力諾國家足球隊|聖馬利諾]]的比賽踢進了自己的第一個國際進球，幫助英格蘭隊以5-0獲得勝利。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2021/mar/25/james-ward-prowse-scuttles-shines-lay-down-euros-marker-england-san-marino|title=Ward-Prowse scuttles and shines to lay down Euros marker for England|date=2021-03-25|accessdate=2021-03-26|work=The Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330155711/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2021/mar/25/james-ward-prowse-scuttles-shines-lay-down-euros-marker-england-san-marino|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==风格特色==
沃德-普勞斯以出色的任意球技巧和准确性而闻名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/nov/05/james-ward-prowse-free-kick-technique-england-southampton |title=If I put the ball where I want to, no keeper can save it |first=David| last=Hytner|date=5 November 2020 |website=The Guardian |access-date=13 December 2020}}</ref>。他保持[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|南安普顿足球俱乐部]]在英超的任意球进球记录，且拥有这项赛事中自2003年以来最高的任意球进球转化率<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/54773207 |title=James Ward-Prowse: Is Southampton midfielder the new Premier League free-kick king? |date=1 November 2020 |website=BBC Sport |access-date=13 December 2020}}</ref>，被认为是当今足坛顶级定位球专家之一<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/29212/12146448/james-ward-prowse-shows-his-set-piece-class-for-southampton-against-manchester-united |title=James Ward-Prowse shows his set-piece class for Southampton against Manchester United |first=Peter |last=Smith |date=29 November 2020|website=Sky Sports |access-date=13 December 2020}}</ref>。他也因其出色的健康水平和耐力而广受赞誉。2021年，他更成为首位连续两个英超赛季打满每一分钟的球员<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://stmarysmusings.sbnation.com/2021/5/23/22450040/report-southampton-lose-at-west-ham|title=REPORT: Southampton lose at West Ham|website=stmarysmusings.sbnation.com/}}</ref>。

